57
00:03:19,145 --> 00:03:20,670
which is Cameroon.

58
00:03:20,870 --> 00:03:25,157
The Ministry of Health is in charge
of the public hospitals, 

59
00:03:25,660 --> 00:03:27,085
and it's job-to-be-done

60
00:03:27,285 --> 00:03:30,760
is to provide the population with
access to health care

61
00:03:30,960 --> 00:03:32,960
including diagnostic capabilities.

62
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:36,248
